title: Ep 293 - Dance Till  You Drop
shortDesc: The celebrations continue as Taarak continues to pick chits from the bowl. The dance continues all night and Taarak notices a small glitch. Meanwhile, Jethalal is hoping he could dance with Babitha. Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 294 - Jethalals Dream Come True
shortDesc: Jethalal finally gets a chance to dance and he is delighted to dance with Babita. Will Iyer be happy about it or jealous of it? Watch this episode and find out.

title: Ep 295 - The Ladies Fool Their Husbands
shortDesc: At the after-party, the ladies decide to serve iced tea instead of alcohol to prove it to them that they don't need alcohol to have fun. The next morning, Jethalal feels very lazy but, Daya wants him to be more active.

title: Ep 296 - Popatlal Is Angry
shortDesc: When everyone in the society wakes up happy on new years, Popatlal gets out of the house half naked and starts screaming for justice. How will everyone react? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 297 - Popatlal VS Bhide
shortDesc: When Popatlal creates a problem early in the morning, everyone in the society gets disturbed. Later, Anjali shares with her lady friends about the funny incident that happened in her house.

title: Ep 298 - Taarak Invites Everyone To The Garden Early In the Morning
shortDesc: Taarak has something planned up his sleeves and he invites everyone in the society at the garden. Jethalal is very unhappy about losing sleep and attending a meeting early in the morning. Will he attend the meet?

title: Ep 299 - Gokuldham Laughing Club
shortDesc: Taarak Mehta arranges for a laughing session early in the morning. Jetha gets disappointed because he would have to give up his sleep.Later, Jetha and Champaklal share their memories with Tappu.

title: Ep 300 - Gadas Go To Ahmedabad
shortDesc: Sundarlal sends a letter to the Gadas inviting them to Ahmedabad. While the family is very excited, Jetha is not even close to being interested. Jethalal comes up with a plan to escape the trip. What is the plan? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 301 - The Bitter Sweet Welcome
shortDesc: When the Gadas reach Ahmedabad, the entire colony welcomes Daya and her family which makes her nostalgic. But, her mother doesn't show up to welcome them. Where is Daya's mother?

title: Ep 302 - Makar Sankranti Celebrations
shortDesc: While the Gadas are spending their Makar Sankranti in Ahmedabad, Gokuldham residents celebrate it together and plan on having lunch together after the celebration. Watch this episode to see their celebration.

title: Ep 303 - The Disappointing Roadtrip
shortDesc: The Gadas decide to return home from Ahmedabad. Jetha faces a problem in booking tickets and hence, they decide to come by road. Will the family be angry at Jethalal for this unfortunate situation? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 304 - Laughter Is The Best Medicine
shortDesc: The members of the society have started to gather in the garden area to laugh and stay healthy. This new laughter club has made everyone realize how important it is to be happy.

title: Ep 305 - Dr. Hathis Laughter Attack
shortDesc: after the laughing session at the laughter club, Dr. Hathi gets a laughter attack which surprises all the residents. Taarak comes up with a plan to stop Hathi's laughter. Will the plan work? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 306 - Republic Day Preparations
shortDesc: When Tappu asks his father to take him to watch a movie, Champaklal doesn't allow them to do so. He says that everyone should celebrate Republic Day with pride. Watch this episode to know more.

title: Ep 307 - The Best Republic Day Speech
shortDesc: On the occasion of republic day, everyone in the society is asked to prepare a speech on the nation. Who would give the best speech? Will Jetha defeat Iyer? Watch to find out.
